column2: SELECT star.apstar_id, star.apogee_id, star.ra, star.dec, star.glon, star.glat, star.apogee_target1, star.apogee_target2, aspcap.teff, aspcap.logg, aspcap.m_h, star.vhelio_avg into mydb.MyTable from apogeeStar star JOIN fGetNearbyApogeeStarEq (#, #, #) near on star.apstar_id = near.apstar_id JOIN aspcapStar aspcap on aspcap.apstar_id = star.apstar_id
